		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Burying the cog in the sand in your hand, you dump it all out and the grains shimmer and fade. As does the target.&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The target ceases to exist until the beginning of its next respective turn, and pops back into being when that happens. During this time the space it occupied is empty, and it cannot be targeted by spells or effects. If its space has become occupied, the target is shunted to the nearest available safe space when it returns.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-c9cb71c6-7fff-6bf9-0373-1a67e044a9b9\">Cast at Higher Levels.</strong> When you use a spell of 2nd level or higher to cast this spell the target instead ceases to exist for 2 rounds. And one additional round for every spell slot above 2nd.</p>",
